title: 111: Crazy Chicks for Me!
description: Cinnabon, Volcanos & crazy chicks. This is how Sal, Adam and Justin celebrated Independence Day. Of course, the one who partied the hardest and had the most fun was #BusyDoingCoolShit Adam, right? Actually, you may be surprised to find out who went off the rails.
